data.description: The perfect home in the perfect neighborhood! True 5 bed, 3 full bath home in a small, secluded, completed gated neighborhood. The home has been extensively updated throughout! Custom, high end kitchen with double gas ovens, gas stove, under counter high capacity ice maker, reverse osmosis tap on main sink, beverage fridge, vegetable sink in island, custom built ins, giant pantry, and more! Laundry room is large with lots of built ins and storage. Large 3 car garage with tons of storage that stays with home. Home has top of the line water filtration with whole home filter, water softener, and UV light sterilization. Large master suite with double shower heads and large jetted tub in the master bath. Large playroom upstairs along with 3 large secondary bedrooms and a full bathroom. Owned top of the line security system with wifi garage door openers, doorbell camera and smart home integration. Giant custom patio with grill and hot tub hookups, garden area with 7 raised beds already growing organic veggies, blackberry bushes, and various fruit trees (peach, plum, apple, nectarine) make this a perfect homesteading paradise! Large attic with multiple upstairs entry points that could be converted to additional living space. Major HVAC and septic components are all new in the last 2 years. Neighborhood is shop approved and perfect for families. Logan county taxes with Edmond school boundaries make this house right in the sweet spot! Houses in this neighborhood don’t last long.
